{"cid":"1576208565560333","cha_name":"肖战","desc":"肖战，1991年10月5日出生于重庆市，中国内地男演员、歌手。\n2015年，以选手的身份参加浙江卫视才艺养成选秀节目《燃烧吧少年》。2016年4月，主演校园星座超能力网络剧《超星星学园》。2018年4月25日，古装奇幻网络剧《哦！我的皇帝陛下》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭北堂墨染一角崭露头角。2019年6月27日，领衔主演的古装仙侠剧《陈情令》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭魏无羡一角赢得广泛关注。7月，主演的古装玄幻剧《斗罗大陆》正式杀青。8月，主演都市情感剧《余生，请多指教》。9月13日，主演的古装仙侠电影《诛仙I》在全国上映。2020年1月24日，肖战首次登上中央广播电视总台春节联欢晚会，与谢娜等合作表演小品《喜欢你，喜欢我》。2月2日，参与演唱的抗疫主题歌曲《坚信爱会赢》及MV正式首发。4月25日零点，歌曲《光点》正式上线。11月19日，参演的古装言情传奇剧《狼殿下》播出，肖战在剧中饰演落拓不羁的赏金猎人疾冲。\n现有待播剧：《余生，请多指教》、《斗罗大陆》。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1576208565560333","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone": 中国煤矿文工团青年演奏员，毕业于中国音乐学院，师承侯彦秋、左继承教授。
      曾代表学院、文工团出访美国、西班牙、葡萄牙、捷克、新加坡等几十个国家。
      曾与高进、凤凰传奇、庞龙、李泉、黄小琥等多个演员合作唢呐配乐。
      曾与卞留念、黄洋、刘卓（中国好声音音乐总编）等老师合作，为其作品唢呐编曲部分配乐。
      曾为舞台剧《骆驼祥子》、《简氏夫人》、《龙须沟》、电影《鼠胆英雄》的唢呐编曲部分配乐。

{"cid":"1576208565560333","cha_name":"肖战","desc":"肖战，1991年10月5日出生于重庆市，中国内地男演员、歌手。\n2015年，以选手的身份参加浙江卫视才艺养成选秀节目《燃烧吧少年》。2016年4月，主演校园星座超能力网络剧《超星星学园》。2018年4月25日，古装奇幻网络剧《哦！我的皇帝陛下》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭北堂墨染一角崭露头角。2019年6月27日，领衔主演的古装仙侠剧《陈情令》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭魏无羡一角赢得广泛关注。7月，主演的古装玄幻剧《斗罗大陆》正式杀青。8月，主演都市情感剧《余生，请多指教》。9月13日，主演的古装仙侠电影《诛仙I》在全国上映。2020年1月24日，肖战首次登上中央广播电视总台春节联欢晚会，与谢娜等合作表演小品《喜欢你，喜欢我》。2月2日，参与演唱的抗疫主题歌曲《坚信爱会赢》及MV正式首发。4月25日零点，歌曲《光点》正式上线。11月19日，参演的古装言情传奇剧《狼殿下》播出，肖战在剧中饰演落拓不羁的赏金猎人疾冲。\n现有待播剧：《余生，请多指教》、《斗罗大陆》。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1576208565560333","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3-dy-ipv6-test.byteimg.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","b {"cid":"1661986683079688","cha_name":"大话西游直播","desc":"至尊宝（周星驰饰）被月光宝盒带回到五百年前，遇见紫霞仙子（朱茵饰），被对方打上烙印成为了对方的人，并发觉自己已变成孙悟空。\n紫霞与青霞（朱茵饰）本是如来佛祖座前日月神灯的灯芯（白天是紫霞，晚上是青霞），二人虽然同一肉身却仇恨颇深，因此紫霞立下誓言，谁能拔出她手中的紫青宝剑，谁就是她的意中人。\n紫青宝剑被至尊宝于不经意间拔出，紫霞决定以身相许，却遭一心记挂白晶晶（莫文蔚饰）的至尊宝拒绝。后牛魔王（陆树铭饰）救下迷失在沙漠中的紫霞，并逼紫霞与他成婚，关键时刻，至尊宝现身。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1661986683079688","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token"
